
                      ░ Duris DikuMUD - INFO Main Menu░

  Type:                   Produces:

  INFO....................This screen
  INFO GODS...............Outline of the Time of Troubles
  INFO <god_name>.........Information about that god. Covers alignment,
                          background (if available), race, and general
                          information.
  INFO ROLE PLAYING.......Information and guidelines for role playing

  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  The INFO file will be updated periodically with more gods and information
  to make your role playing efforts here in the Realms more enjoyable.

  Information about the various mobs (monsters) will be added in the future
  to give a general idea of what the mob looks like, and stories behind it,
  and how it lives from day to day on Toril.
